{"id":642874,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/04/【敏感词库】后主/","date":"2020-04-30T04:29:43Z","modified":"2020-04-30T04:36:04Z","title":"【敏感词库】后主","content":"<p>4月28日，有<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RealEmperorPooh/status/1255104151790338048\">网友反馈</a>在闲鱼（阿里巴巴旗下的二手闲置品交易平台）意外发现一段涉及主板的交易信息无法正常发出，进而发现“后主”一词竟被列为禁发敏感词。很显然该词的设置与习近平有关。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642875\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWsGgvLU0AEq3dX.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWsGgvLU0AEq3dX.jpeg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWsGgvLU0AEq3dX-150x300.jpeg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWsGgvLU0AEq3dX-512x1024.jpeg 512w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642877\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWsGhIwUEAAv892-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWsGhIwUEAAv892-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWsGhIwUEAAv892-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWsGhIwUEAAv892-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWsGhIwUEAAv892-1080x810.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWsGhIwUEAAv892.jpg 1242w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642876\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWsGhIwUEAAv89_-1024x513.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"250\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWsGhIwUEAAv89_-1024x513.jpeg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWsGhIwUEAAv89_-300x150.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWsGhIwUEAAv89_-768x385.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWsGhIwUEAAv89_.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>关于“后主”一词的解释有“后代的君主、嗣君”、“王朝的末代君主”两种，而网民更常使用的往往是后者，即“末代君主”。</p>\n<blockquote><p>后主一词始出自《三国志》，作者陈寿曾在蜀汉为官，因此在编写《三国志·蜀书》的时候，就称刘备为先主，刘禅为后主，后来人们将与刘禅有相似经历的，被俘的割据政权末代君主均称为后主。</p></blockquote>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642878\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWsGh1gUcAEdp42.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWsGh1gUcAEdp42.jpeg 680w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWsGh1gUcAEdp42-300x224.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>截至发稿时（北京时间2020年4月30日 12:10分）已有多名网友对此进行了测试，证实该情况的真实性。</p>\n<p>网友恶搞图：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642881\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWvgSe7X0AAgOkf-648x1024.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWvgSe7X0AAgOkf-648x1024.jpeg 648w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWvgSe7X0AAgOkf-190x300.jpeg 190w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWvgSe7X0AAgOkf-768x1214.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EWvgSe7X0AAgOkf.jpeg 810w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"eGJ53hml6u\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/%e3%80%90%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e8%af%8d%e5%ba%93%e3%80%91%e7%bf%a0%e4%b8%8e%e7%a5%88%e7%bf%a0%e8%b6%85%e8%af%9d/\">【敏感词库】“翠”与“祈翠超话”</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《【敏感词库】“翠”与“祈翠超话”》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/%e3%80%90%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e8%af%8d%e5%ba%93%e3%80%91%e7%bf%a0%e4%b8%8e%e7%a5%88%e7%bf%a0%e8%b6%85%e8%af%9d/embed/#?secret=eGJ53hml6u\" data-secret=\"eGJ